title: (2015) Slynk - Front Yard Futon (SectionZ Records - SZLP0035)
description:
Hey guys.
Thanks for stealing my album. I understand not all of you can afford to buy it and that's cool. That's why I'm uploading my album here myself.

All I ask in return is that you help spread the word about the album and about my music. If you could click a like/share/follow/repost button on one or all of the following social media sites, I'd be very grateful.
